1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,212
=Episode 17=

3
00:00:53,079 --> 00:00:55,119
What do you say, Master Yu?

4
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:57,520
What am I supposed to say?

5
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,799
Don't talk nonsense.

6
00:00:58,799 --> 00:00:59,960
Be responsible for what you say.

7
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,679
Before the golden pearl
was placed in Mr. Qin's hand,

8
00:01:02,679 --> 00:01:04,300
you were the only one who touched it.

9
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:06,662
Why don't we search you and see?

10
00:01:08,159 --> 00:01:08,719
Search me?

11
00:01:09,159 --> 00:01:10,470
Let's see who dares to search me.

12
00:01:10,487 --> 00:01:11,760
Searching me is illegal.

13
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:12,680
What right do you have?

14
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,400
Search him!

15
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:14,890
A body search is against the law!

16
00:01:14,959 --> 00:01:15,959
You're breaking the law!

17
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:22,200
Look!

18
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:27,920
Check it.

19
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:30,900
Yes, this is the one.

20
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,680
This is the golden pearl
from the auction.

21
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:35,239
There's a tiny natural dent here.

22
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,120
We have photos and videos

23
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:39,159
from the appraisal to prove it.

24
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:40,719
Yu Jinghai,

25
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,762
how dare you deceive me?

26
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,519
Explain yourself!

27
00:01:44,879 --> 00:01:45,680
It wasn't me.

28
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,719
It was him!

29
00:01:47,239 --> 00:01:49,280
When he snatched the pearl from you

30
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,439
and smashed it earlier,

31
00:01:50,439 --> 00:01:52,159
he secretly swapped the real one.

32
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,959
Now he's framing me!

33
00:01:55,312 --> 00:01:57,672
You're not just
a fake master playing tricks.

34
00:01:57,719 --> 00:01:59,719
You're also great at twisting the truth.

35
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:00,400
Pah!

36
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,000
You're the one twisting the truth!

37
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,879
Let me get up.

38
00:02:02,879 --> 00:02:03,830
Let him get up and talk.

39
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,519
I, Yu Jinghai,

40
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,760
founded the Xuanji Hall

41
00:02:08,079 --> 00:02:09,519
decades ago.

42
00:02:09,519 --> 00:02:11,275
I've helped countless people
and never taken a single penny.

43
00:02:11,275 --> 00:02:12,040
My reputation speaks for itself.

44
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,319
In Jinzhou, everyone

45
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:14,439
knows my name!

46
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,400
That's right!

47
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,800
I can vouch for Master Yu!

48
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:18,479
I even tried to give him my watch once,

49
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,190
and he refused it.

50
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,319
It's you.

51
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,360
You're behind this.

52
00:02:22,660 --> 00:02:23,639
You want my sister dead.

53
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:24,599
Exactly.

54
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,390
Master Yu has extraordinary abilities.

55
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,590
Why would he do something like this?

56
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:29,400
He would never do such a thing.

57
00:02:29,712 --> 00:02:30,633
If anything, Ye Chen

58
00:02:30,633 --> 00:02:31,672
looks more like a fraud.

59
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,639
That's right.

60
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:33,360
Fine.

61
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:33,680
Fraud!

62
00:02:33,919 --> 00:02:35,919
A miracle-working master, huh?

63
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:36,560
Fine.

64
00:02:37,199 --> 00:02:38,919
I'm going to expose you
completely today.

65
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,159
Expose him?

66
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:40,919
That's ridiculous.

67
00:02:41,199 --> 00:02:42,599
Shut up.

68
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,280
You're the biggest fool here.

69
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,479
You don't even realize
you're being used.

70
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,120
Dad, don't listen to his nonsense.

71
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,199
Qin Aodong,

72
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,360
you don't actually
think the fang hanging

73
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,599
from your waist

74
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:54,759
is Wolf Fang Talisman, do you?

75
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:55,987
Wait.

76
00:02:59,250 --> 00:03:00,120
What else would it be?

77
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,840
Take a closer look.

78
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:04,159
Isn't it smaller
than a normal wolf fang?

79
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,520
So... what?

80
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:08,960
Maybe

81
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,000
wolves were smaller back

82
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,280
in the Three Kingdoms era.

83
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:13,879
Wolves

84
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,680
chew meat and bones,

85
00:03:16,237 --> 00:03:18,187
so their tooth roots
are usually round and full.

86
00:03:18,187 --> 00:03:18,867
Look at this one.

87
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:20,150
Does it look round to you?

88
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,280
The wear isn't right either.

89
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,000
That's true.

90
00:03:23,350 --> 00:03:24,070
In my opinion,

91
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:25,840
it's just a dog's canine tooth.

92
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:28,212
Who knows which dead dog's mouth
it was pulled from.

93
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:31,719
Yu Jinghai,

94
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,319
why did you lie to me?

95
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:34,950
You believe him
just because he said so?

96
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:38,439
That day at your house, you saw me
set up the altar, perform the exorcism,

97
00:03:38,439 --> 00:03:39,599
and treat your sister,

98
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,240
you saw it with your own eyes.

99
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,439
Could that have been fake?

100
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,199
That's true.

101
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:45,840
Dad, you saw it too.

102
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,439
He...

103
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,120
You shut up!

104
00:03:47,562 --> 00:03:49,921
It's just clear water turning black,

105
00:03:49,921 --> 00:03:51,787
black water turning clear,

106
00:03:51,825 --> 00:03:54,585
blood from an iron sword
on yellow paper,

107
00:03:55,090 --> 00:03:56,390
candles lighting by themselves.

108
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,639
Believe it or not,

109
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:01,479
I can also perform
all of Master Yu's tricks.

110
00:04:02,159 --> 00:04:03,900
You? That's impossible!

111
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:06,080
Why don't we step outside?

112
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,560
Let me demonstrate for everyone.

113
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,120
Yu Jinghai,

114
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:11,000
do you dare?

115
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,439
It really turned black!

116
00:04:32,090 --> 00:04:32,959
He really knows magic.

117
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:33,959
Look.

118
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:34,920
It really turned black.

119
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:37,120
Looks like the Treasures Pavilion
is full of bad energy.

120
00:04:38,879 --> 00:04:39,439
Sword!

121
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:52,959
Clear!

122
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,439
- The water turned clear again.
- It really did.

123
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,439
What is going on?

124
00:04:57,850 --> 00:04:59,199
Isn't that Master Yu's technique?

125
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:00,800
How can he do it too?

126
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,920
- Could he also be a master?
- Exactly.

127
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:06,040
These are nothing more than cheap tricks

128
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,987
meant to fool people.

129
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,900
The "master" you all believe in

130
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:12,160
is just an amateur chemistry enthusiast.

131
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,560
Turning clear water black

132
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,737
simply means
adding a little ferrous sulfate

133
00:05:16,839 --> 00:05:18,399
while no one is looking.

134
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:19,720
Turning it clear again

135
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,600
just means adding some oxalic acid,

136
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:23,800
which produces the effect you see now.

137
00:05:24,839 --> 00:05:26,199
As for the yellow paper bleeding

138
00:05:26,199 --> 00:05:27,360
when struck by the sword,

139
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,920
the paper was soaked in turmeric water,

140
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,470
and the sword was sprayed
with an alkaline solution.

141
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:33,800
A chemical reaction occurs when turmeric
meets an alkaline solution,

142
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,387
turning it blood red.

143
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,690
Candles lighting themselves
is even simpler.

144
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:39,160
You only need to soak the wick

145
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:40,079
in carbon disulfide

146
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:41,879
that contains
dissolved white phosphorus.

147
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:44,062
Carbon disulfide
evaporates quickly in the air,

148
00:05:44,137 --> 00:05:46,112
and the white phosphorus
ignites on its own.

149
00:05:47,350 --> 00:05:48,470
So that is how it works.

150
00:05:48,470 --> 00:05:49,870
Yu Jinghai tricked us.

151
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,800
Master, my feet!

152
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,937
He is just a fraud!

153
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:52,720
Fraud! Fraud!

154
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:55,120
- Fraud!
- Fraud!

155
00:05:55,639 --> 00:05:58,875
But after I performed the ritual
at the Qin residence last time,

156
00:05:58,875 --> 00:06:01,519
Ms. Qin's condition really did improve.

157
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,079
How do you explain that?

158
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:04,590
Still refusing to admit it?

159
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:05,399
Fine.

160
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,839
Then I will show you.

161
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:35,720
Master!

162
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:36,639
Master!

163
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:38,279
As everyone just saw,

164
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:41,600
I only needed to add some rosemary

165
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:44,487
and a few other stimulating herbs
to the talisman paper.

166
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,900
Anyone who inhales it
will feel a brief surge of energy.

167
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:49,240
Aoxue was the same.

168
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,300
The sudden stimulation

169
00:06:51,310 --> 00:06:52,780
made it seem like
her condition improved,

170
00:06:52,790 --> 00:06:53,950
but once the effect wears off,

171
00:06:53,962 --> 00:06:55,574
her illness will become worse.

172
00:06:57,639 --> 00:06:59,279
Thanks for watching Approaching Science.

173
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:00,079
Isn't that harming her?

174
00:07:00,079 --> 00:07:02,425
Next up is Law in Action.

175
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,160
Yu Jinghai,

176
00:07:05,590 --> 00:07:06,560
do you admit your guilt?

177
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:07,959
I...

178
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,959
You what?

179
00:07:09,010 --> 00:07:11,462
You had bad intentions
the moment you approached Qin Aodong.

180
00:07:11,462 --> 00:07:13,103
You were after the South Sea Gold Pearl.

181
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:15,959
All that talk about curing Qin Aoxue
and driving away evil spirits

182
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:16,875
was complete nonsense!

183
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:18,079
You frightened Qin Gang

184
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,399
into bidding for that pearl,

185
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:22,900
but you already had a fake prepared
so you could secretly switch it.

186
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,839
There is still hope.

187
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:27,959
Yu Jinghai,

188
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,720
Qin Aoxue was poisoned.

189
00:07:30,399 --> 00:07:31,439
Was that your doing?

190
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,040
No, no.

191
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:34,920
It was not me.

192
00:07:34,930 --> 00:07:36,079
I really did not poison anyone.

193
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:36,680
I...

194
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,319
I only wanted money.

195
00:07:38,319 --> 00:07:39,600
I would never take a life.

196
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:41,759
Back then it was Xiao Weiwei

197
00:07:41,759 --> 00:07:43,319
who asked me for a favor.

198
00:07:43,319 --> 00:07:45,279
She wanted me to trick Qin Aodong
out of a little money.

199
00:07:45,279 --> 00:07:46,639
Then Qin Aodong told me

200
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:48,040
his sister had a strange illness,

201
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:51,040
so I thought I could use her illness
to get that pearl.

202
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:51,600
I...

203
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,639
I only wanted money.

204
00:07:53,639 --> 00:07:55,160
I would never poison anyone.

205
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,920
Mr. Qin's son is a fool.

206
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,079
He believes whatever you say.

207
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,590
- Who are you calling a fool?
- Enough, Dong.

208
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,639
Control yourself.

209
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:03,839
Yu Jinghai,

210
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:06,680
I truly did not expect you
to do something like this.

211
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,839
I will be honest with you.

212
00:08:09,380 --> 00:08:10,480
Before we came out just now,

213
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,780
I had already called the police.

214
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,680
If you have anything to say,

215
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,519
you can explain it
at the police station.

216
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:16,720
You called the police?

217
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:18,920
You actually called the police?

218
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:21,480
I should be the one calling!

219
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,375
I'm reporting you to the police!

220
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,839
Trying to leave now?

221
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,000
It is too late.

222
00:08:26,090 --> 00:08:27,187
Stay right where you are.

223
00:08:32,920 --> 00:08:33,560
Ye Chen,

224
00:08:33,560 --> 00:08:34,560
you brat.

225
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:37,262
I planned that scheme so perfectly,

226
00:08:37,262 --> 00:08:39,325
yet you ruined it so easily.

227
00:08:39,519 --> 00:08:40,639
If it were not for you,

228
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,799
I would already be abroad

229
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:45,480
enjoying the rest of my life
with that golden pearl.

230
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,600
You ruined everything for me.

231
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,950
I won't let you get away with this.

232
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,320
Yu Jinghai,

233
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,675
do you believe
that I actually know magic?

234
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:57,480
I could summon thunder
and strike you down.

235
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,360
There is no such thing as magic.

236
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:02,519
I do know a bit of martial arts though.

237
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,480
Today we will see whether you strike me
with lightning first

238
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:08,360
or I cut you down with my sword.

239
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:13,960
Thunder!

240
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:34,600
That was powerful!

241
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,639
Please forgive us.

242
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:37,720
We were ignorant!

243
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,919
He killed someone!

244
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:40,679
Master, please take me as your disciple.

245
00:09:40,679 --> 00:09:41,840
Please bless me.

246
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,320
Call an ambulance.

247
00:09:43,660 --> 00:09:45,200
Mr. Ye, that was an impressive move.

248
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:47,080
Every step Yu Jinghai took

249
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,039
was within your calculations, wasn't it?

250
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,519
Yu Jinghai was deceiving people
from the start.

251
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:53,879
Then he became furious

252
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:55,990
and tried to draw lightning onto himself
with the iron sword.

253
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,639
If Mr. Ye had not intervened just now,

254
00:09:57,780 --> 00:09:59,679
he would have been reduced
to a charred corpse.

255
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,960
There is a legendary technique

256
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,039
called Aura Observation.

257
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:04,519
Those who master it

258
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:07,360
can sense thunder,
draw thunder, and release thunder.

259
00:10:08,250 --> 00:10:10,965
Mr. Ye precisely
calculated the path of the lightning

260
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,440
and used the technique

261
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,037
to disperse part of the strike,

262
00:10:14,037 --> 00:10:15,275
which saved Yu Jinghai's life.

263
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,200
Mr. Ye

264
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:21,000
is the true master here.

265
00:10:22,050 --> 00:10:22,879
You have heard of it?

266
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:24,279
Yes, I have heard of it.

267
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,919
Thank you, Ms. Song,
for speaking up for me.

268
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:31,799
You're too polite, Mr. Ye.

269
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:34,559
You helped
defend Treasures Pavilion's reputation.

270
00:10:35,090 --> 00:10:36,440
I should be the one thanking you.

271
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:37,440
If you ever

272
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,320
need help in the future,

273
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:40,600
please feel free to come to me.

274
00:10:41,639 --> 00:10:42,120
Goodbye.

275
00:10:56,279 --> 00:10:56,879
Ye Chen.

276
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:05,790
- Why...
- Don't touch me.

277
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:09,450
(Heaven grants me power
to command all spirits,)

278
00:11:09,460 --> 00:11:11,390
(and the thunder of the earth
gathers within me.)

279
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,820
If dark storm clouds begin piling up,

280
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:23,679
thunder will definitely follow.

281
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,960
(Affected by the northwest
high-attitude flow.)

282
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:28,919
Master, this Aura Observation technique
is quite interesting.

283
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,240
If I learn it,

284
00:11:30,559 --> 00:11:33,440
does that mean I won't need
to watch the weather forecast anymore?

285
00:11:33,799 --> 00:11:34,799
More or less.

286
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,600
Neither of them is very accurate.

287
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:38,650
Day and night temperatures vary greatly.

288
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:39,440
The air is dry.

289
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:40,320
The wind is light.

290
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:40,960
Overall...

291
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,240
Thunder is coming.

292
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,240
Everyone should take note.

293
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,039
Master,

294
00:11:46,279 --> 00:11:47,519
you are amazing.

295
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,799
So that is how it works.

296
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:53,200
Then you really should thank Mr. Quan.

297
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,320
When I was young,

298
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,320
he forced me to learn it.

299
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:57,879
Back then I was still a kid,

300
00:11:58,020 --> 00:12:00,279
I thought the old man
was just making my life miserable.

301
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:03,380
I never expected it would come in handy
now that I am older.

302
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:06,480
But speaking of that,

303
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:08,840
if you ever run into something
that dangerous again,

304
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,399
you must protect yourself first.

305
00:12:10,639 --> 00:12:11,679
Do not act recklessly.

306
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:15,720
Do not worry, Churan.

307
00:12:15,919 --> 00:12:16,639
I know my limits.

308
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:20,919
But then again,

309
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,720
even though it was my first time

310
00:12:23,039 --> 00:12:24,519
meeting Song Wanting,

311
00:12:24,837 --> 00:12:26,462
she saw straight through my move.

312
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:31,120
I heard that old man from her family

313
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:33,080
has not appeared in public
for many years.

314
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,200
She is still so young

315
00:12:35,679 --> 00:12:37,679
and already able
to manage such a huge business.

316
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,440
She is not simple.

317
00:12:42,487 --> 00:12:44,952
This is the first time I have seen you
admire someone so much.

318
00:12:45,260 --> 00:12:46,425
No, that's not what I meant.

319
00:12:46,559 --> 00:12:46,879
I...

320
00:12:46,879 --> 00:12:47,919
I have no other intentions.

321
00:12:47,919 --> 00:12:48,960
I just admire her abilities.

322
00:12:49,025 --> 00:12:50,466
We only met today.

323
00:12:50,466 --> 00:12:51,600
Do I mean anything else?

324
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:55,919
You are gentle, beautiful,
virtuous, and graceful.

325
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:57,279
I was being narrow minded.

326
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:04,720
Grandpa,

327
00:13:06,279 --> 00:13:07,679
I underestimated Ye Chen.

328
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,919
He is not as simple as I thought.

329
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:18,200
Ye Chen has been improving very quickly.

330
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:21,159
He also has close ties with Dihao.

331
00:13:22,279 --> 00:13:23,240
His surname is Ye.

332
00:13:25,037 --> 00:13:26,557
Whether it is a coincidence or not,

333
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,240
it is all very intriguing.

334
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:31,240
Grandpa,

335
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,759
you once taught me this.

336
00:13:35,290 --> 00:13:36,720
We should always plan ahead of time.

337
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:01,488
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

338
00:14:01,575 --> 00:14:05,328
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

339
00:14:05,788 --> 00:14:10,725
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

340
00:14:10,888 --> 00:14:13,175
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

341
00:14:13,488 --> 00:14:16,168
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

342
00:14:17,238 --> 00:14:19,863
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

343
00:14:20,163 --> 00:14:23,175
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

344
00:14:23,375 --> 00:14:26,425
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

345
00:14:26,538 --> 00:14:29,500
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

346
00:14:29,768 --> 00:14:32,925
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

347
00:14:33,150 --> 00:14:36,900
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

348
00:14:36,900 --> 00:14:39,763
♪I belong to no one♪

349
00:14:39,825 --> 00:14:43,275
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

350
00:14:43,275 --> 00:14:45,950
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

351
00:14:45,950 --> 00:14:52,288
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
